{% block content %}

  <article>

    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-header-inner">
        <a href="/services/" class="post-breadcrumb">&larr; All Services</a>
        <span class="blog-category">Service</span>
        <h1>Your Business Is Losing Leads Right Now. We Fix That.</h1>
        <div class="post-meta">
          <span>By <strong>Freeland Marketing &amp; Entertainment</strong></span>
          <span>Palm Coast, FL</span>
          <span>Serving Businesses Nationwide</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="post-featured-img">
      <picture>
        <img src="/blog/images/service-ai-automation.jpg" alt="24/7 AI lead capture system for businesses — never miss another lead" width="860" height="480" />
      </picture>
    </div>

    <div class="post-body">

      <p style="font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.7;">A customer visits your website at 9pm. Nobody is there to answer. They leave. A homeowner calls your business on Saturday morning. It goes to voicemail. They call the next company on Google. A lead fills out your contact form on Sunday. By Monday when you respond, they have already hired someone else.</p>

      <p><strong>This is happening to your business every single week.</strong> And every missed inquiry is revenue going straight to your competitor.</p>

      <h2>The Problem No One Talks About</h2>

      <ul class="pain-list">
        <li>62% of calls to businesses go unanswered during busy hours and after 5pm</li>
        <li>Leads that wait more than 5 minutes for a response are 21x less likely to convert</li>
        <li>A business doing $50K/month is losing an estimated $10,000-$20,000 in revenue from missed after-hours inquiries</li>
        <li>Hiring a receptionist costs $35,000-$45,000/year — and they still only work 40 hours a week</li>
        <li>Your website gets traffic at night and on weekends when nobody is there to convert it</li>
      </ul>

      <p>You are already paying for the marketing that drives these leads to you — ads, SEO, social media, word of mouth. But if no one is there to catch them when they arrive, that marketing spend is wasted.</p>

      <h2>What Our AI Lead Capture System Does</h2>

      <p>We install an AI-powered system that works across your website, phone line, and SMS — answering every inquiry instantly, qualifying leads automatically, and booking appointments directly into your calendar. It works 24 hours a day, 7 days a week, 365 days a year.</p>

      <div class="stat-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">20-40%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">More leads captured in the first month</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">200%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Increase in after-hours appointment bookings</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">10x</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Less expensive than hiring additional staff</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-number">3-6 mo</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Average payback period from recovered revenue</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>How It Works</h2>

      <ol>
        <li><strong>Website AI chatbot</strong> — a trained assistant on your website that greets visitors, answers questions about your services and pricing, captures contact information, and books appointments — all in a natural conversation</li>
        <li><strong>AI phone answering</strong> — missed calls are answered by an AI voice agent that sounds natural, answers common questions, captures caller details, and can transfer to you when available</li>
        <li><strong>SMS lead follow-up</strong> — every lead that comes in gets an instant text confirmation and follow-up sequence so they stay engaged until you can connect personally</li>
        <li><strong>Automatic appointment booking</strong> — the AI checks your real-time calendar availability and books appointments without any back-and-forth</li>
        <li><strong>Daily lead summary</strong> — every morning you get a report of every lead captured overnight, every conversation that happened, and every appointment booked</li>
      </ol>

      <p>Your AI assistant is trained specifically on your business — your services, your pricing, your hours, your FAQs. It does not give generic answers. It represents your business the way you would.</p>

      <div class="post-callout">
        <p>"We set up an AI assistant for a bed and breakfast with 7 rooms. Phone calls dropped dramatically because the AI handled booking inquiries, room questions, and availability checks instantly — at a fraction of the cost of front desk staff."</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Industries We Serve</h2>

      <div class="industry-grid">
        <div class="industry-item">
          <strong>Contractors &amp; Home Services</strong>
          <span>Capture calls while you are on the job site. Book estimates automatically.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <strong>Dental &amp; Medical Practices</strong>
          <span>200%+ increase in after-hours appointment bookings.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
