          <span>35% more qualified leads, 25% lower cost per lead.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <strong>Restaurants &amp; Hospitality</strong>
          <span>Handle reservation inquiries and event bookings 24/7.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <strong>Law Firms</strong>
          <span>Qualify potential clients and book consultations after hours.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <strong>Salons &amp; Spas</strong>
          <span>Fill appointment slots around the clock without phone tag.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>Flexible Plans for Every Business</h2>

      <p>Every business has different needs — a single-location restaurant and a multi-location service company need very different setups. We offer three tiers that scale with your business:</p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Starter</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:0;">Website lead capture</p>
          <ul>
            <li>AI chatbot on your website</li>
            <li>Lead qualification questions</li>
            <li>Contact info capture</li>
            <li>Email notifications for new leads</li>
            <li>Monthly performance report</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:block;text-align:center;">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card featured">
          <h3>Growth</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:0;">Chat + phone + SMS</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in Starter</li>
            <li>AI phone answering agent</li>
            <li>SMS lead follow-up sequences</li>
            <li>Automatic appointment booking</li>
            <li>Calendar integration</li>
            <li>Daily lead summary emails</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:block;text-align:center;">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Premium</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.9rem;color:#aaa;margin-bottom:0;">Full AI front desk</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Everything in Growth</li>
            <li>CRM integration &amp; lead tracking</li>
            <li>Custom AI training on your business</li>
            <li>Multi-location support</li>
            <li>Analytics dashboard</li>
            <li>Priority support</li>
            <li>Quarterly optimization reviews</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary" style="display:block;text-align:center;">Get a Quote &rarr;</a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <p style="text-align:center;color:#888;font-size:0.9rem;margin-top:1rem;">All plans include setup, training, and ongoing AI updates. No long-term contracts. Book a free consultation and we will recommend the right plan for your business.</p>

      <h2>Why Freeland Marketing</h2>

      <p>We do not just hand you a chatbot and disappear. We design the entire lead capture system around how your specific business works — your services, your booking flow, your customer questions. We set it up, train the AI on your business, test it, and go live. Then we monitor performance and optimize it every month.</p>

      <p>This connects directly to our full marketing ecosystem. Leads from <a href="/services/google-ads-management/">Google Ads</a> and <a href="/services/seo/">SEO</a> flow into the AI system. Captured leads are fed into <a href="/services/lead-nurturing/">nurturing sequences</a> and <a href="/services/crm-automation/">CRM automation</a>. The result is a complete pipeline from first click to booked appointment — with no gaps where leads fall through.</p>

      <h2>The Math Is Simple</h2>

      <p>If your average customer is worth $500 and the AI system captures just 5 additional leads per month that you were previously losing, that is $2,500 in recovered monthly revenue. Most businesses see payback within the first few months and the ROI only grows from there.</p>

      <div class="post-callout">
        <p>"Speed to lead is one of the highest-leverage variables in business. Companies that respond within 5 minutes are 21x more likely to qualify a lead than those that respond in 30 minutes. AI makes your business the fastest responder every single time."</p>
      </div>

      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <h3>How many leads is my business actually losing?</h3>
      <p>Most businesses lose 20-40% of potential leads from after-hours inquiries, slow response times, and missed calls during busy periods. We can analyze your current traffic and call volume to give you a specific estimate during a free consultation.</p>

      <h3>Will customers know they are talking to AI?</h3>
      <p>The AI is trained on your specific business information and responds naturally. Most customers prefer getting an instant, helpful response over leaving a voicemail and waiting. The system can hand off to a human team member at any time during business hours.</p>

      <h3>How fast is the setup?</h3>
      <p>Most businesses are fully live within 5-7 business days. We handle all configuration, AI training, testing, and deployment. Many clients start capturing recovered leads within the first week.</p>

      <h3>What if I already have a website chatbot?</h3>
      <p>Most generic chatbots are decision-tree bots that frustrate visitors. Our AI is conversational — it understands questions, gives real answers about your business, and guides visitors to take action. It replaces basic chatbots with something that actually converts.</p>

      <h3>Do I need to be technical?</h3>
      <p>Not at all. We handle all the technical setup and management. You just tell us about your business, approve the AI responses, and start receiving leads.</p>

      <h2>Nationwide Service</h2>

      <p>Headquartered in <strong>Palm Coast, FL</strong> and serving businesses across all 50 states. Every system is set up, managed, and optimized remotely — no matter your industry or location.</p>

      <div class="post-cta-box">
        <h3>Find Out How Many Leads You Are Losing</h3>
        <p>Book a free 15-minute consultation. We will look at your current website traffic, call patterns, and response times — then show you exactly how many leads the AI system would recover for your business.</p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary btn-large">Book My Free Consultation &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top:2rem;">Related: <a href="/services/call-center-booking-automation/">Call-Center &amp; Booking Automation</a> | <a href="/services/ai-automation/">AI Automation Services</a> | <a href="/services/lead-nurturing/">Lead Nurturing Sequences</a></p>

      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Related reading: <a href="/blog/how-to-generate-leads-for-your-business/">How to Generate Leads for Your Business</a></p>

